Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(注意：本字幕针对2020年动画版视频,\N与旧版本在对话内容和时间轴上略有差异)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\b1}The Faceless Ones: Episode 1{\b\b}\N{\b1\b1}无面一族: 第一集{\b\b}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是只飞兽!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's a flying beastie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿, 你们, 站住!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hey, you! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,散开!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飞行员说了什么?   - 跑道上有个警察亭\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- The pilot said what?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A police box on the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说得跟真的似的! 让他回到排队区\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A likely story! Tell him to get back into stack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等待下一步安排\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and await further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock 小姐, 接机场警局\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Miss Rock, get the airport police.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,塔台呼叫SDX\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Control. Sugar Delta X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请返回排队区\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Return to stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,警局吗? 我是总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Police? Commandant here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,入港航班报告说有障碍物\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}In-bound aircraft reports obstruction
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说是在第五和第二跑道的交界处\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}on intersection of runways five and two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.69,0:02:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,去调查一下, 汇报情况\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Investigate and report back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.04,0:02:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,警察亭子\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Police box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Jamie! 到我这里来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jamie! Come over here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,把那信封给我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Give me that envelope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你站住\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I would advise you to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你能快点过来吗? 有麻烦了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can you come quickly? Trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦? 发生什么事了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Trouble? What happened?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那些明信片, 有人发现了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The postcards. Someone found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,行了, 行了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们是把它卸在四号机库了, 是个什么东西?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}So you dumped it by number four hangar,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是个警察亭子?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It WAS a police box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接警察局长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get me the police chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 你可以安排那些飞机降落了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right. You can bring those planes down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 障碍已经被清除了  - 好的, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- The obstruction's been cleared. - Right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这是不是一个恶作剧, 先生? 学生什么的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think it was a practical joke, sir?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Students or someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不管他是谁, 一旦被我抓到了, 有他们好果子吃\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, whoever it was, they'll pay for it\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}when I get my hands on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能让这些恶作剧什么的威胁到乘客的安全\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I won't have passengers' lives\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}endangered by practical jokers or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Reynolds 警司吗? 我让总指挥接您电话\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Superintendent Reynolds?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I have the commandant for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,警局总长\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The Chief of Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,听着, 跑道上的警察亭子都是怎么一回事?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Listen, what's all this\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about a police box on the runway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.32,0:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哦...好吧, 各处的安保工作必须加强!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh. Well, security's got to be tightened up all round!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他报告说有人看到四个嫌疑人从那个亭子四散跑开\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He reports that four suspects\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}were seen running away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那抓到了他们吗?   - 没有!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Did they catch them?  - No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这警察够笨的, 给跟丢了, 这会儿都跑出八百里远了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Idiot of a policeman lost them.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're miles away by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接出入境检查站\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get me Immigration.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他们说我想知道有没有人看到些可疑人员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Tell them to let me know\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}if any suspicious characters are seen there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Polly 在那儿!   - Polly! 这边来!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- There's Polly!  - Polly! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,博士...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚看到有人被害了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've just seen a man killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 被一个飞兽给撞了?   - 不是\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Hit by one of the beasties?  - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那里面有两个人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There were two men in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一个手里有枪, 他开枪杀了另外一个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}One of them had a gun,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and he shot the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那个凶手, 他看到你了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The murderer, did he see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他还追我, 但我设法甩掉了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He chased me but I managed to lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能找到那个机库吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Could you find this hangar again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这, 我觉得能...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我还记得名字, 好像叫变色龙什么的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I can remember the name.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It was Chameleon something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ben 去哪儿了?  - 我们没看见他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where's Ben? - We haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快点, 我们去找这个机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Come on, let's find this hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是, 那个有枪的家伙还会找我\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}But, the bloke with the gun will be looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会照顾你的, 来, 快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll look after you. Now, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过..Ben 怎么办?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where's...What about Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他发现了那些明信片  - 他叫什么名字?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He found the postcards.  - His name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道. 我在办公室逮住他的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know. I caught him in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,他已经发现了证据, 我不得不阻止他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He'd found evidence. I had to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀死的是 Gascoigne 督察, 是个警察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You've killed Detective Inspector Gascoigne -\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}a policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得他上面有人派他来的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you think a parent sent him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很有可能. 不过没关系\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Possibly. It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是没人会找到他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The important thing is that nobody should find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,安排人处理掉吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Arrange disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 尽快搞定这事\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}All right. Get it over here as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 箱子已经在来的路上了  - 好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A container is on the way.  - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,销毁这个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Destroy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么把那些行李箱留在这里?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Why have you left those suitcases there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个侦探 - 我被他打断了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The detective - he interrupted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Spencer!​\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Spencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Look.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.32,0:08:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是从那个门里出来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}The bloke came out of that door there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,被锁住了吗? 里面有人吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Is it locked? Is anyone in there?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是锁住的, 里面没有人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}It's locked. There's nobody there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Polly, 那个开枪杀他的家伙...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly, this man who killed him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你还能认出他来吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you recognise him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,能! 他还追我, 我怎么都能认出他来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes! He chased me. I'd recognise him anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Polly, 你说说他是怎么被杀的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly, how would you say he was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用的是枪\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}With a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你能给我描述一下吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Can you describe it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不能, 太远了. 为什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No. It was too far away. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这人是被电死的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This man was electrocuted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他的衣服全都烧焦了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}His clothes are all scorched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是某种枪, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It was definitely some kind of a gun, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧, 但这种枪在这个星球上还没有研发出来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Maybe. But not one that's\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}been developed yet on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这个他们称为博士的人, 他是从哪里了解到这些的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This man they call Doctor,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}where does he get his knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他看起来像是一个普通人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He looks like a normal being.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,比大多数的智力高多了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}More intelligent than most.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我们的行动是一个威胁\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's a threat to our operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我去杀了他  - 不要\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I'll kill him. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先抓那个女孩儿, 她能指认你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Get the girl. She can identify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.90,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以稍后再对付这老头\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We can deal with the man later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他会说出去的  - 那又怎样?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- He may talk.  - So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没人会信他的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Nobody will believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须向当局报告这个事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We must report this to the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那个追我们的人, 我们也许可以找到他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That man who chased us. We could find him maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.04,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么, 那个警察?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What, the policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不, 不, Jamie. 我们必须找到这个地方的总负责人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}No, no, Jamie, we must find\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}the man in charge in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那他怎么办? 我们不能把他扔在这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What about him? We can't just leave him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们做不了什么了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's nothing else we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在还是去找机场主楼吧, 快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now let's find the main airport building. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定这条路对吗, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you sure this is the right way, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是通向主楼的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It seems to lead to the main airport building.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我怎么了?   - 短暂的肌体失能\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What happened to me?  - A temporary disablement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就能恢复正常, 起来吧\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll be back to normal any second now. Up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你要带我去哪里?   - 你马上就知道了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where are you taking me?  - You'll soon find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我抓住她了  - 非常好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I've got her.  - Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.78,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这次没人看见你吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did anybody see you this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她走在她朋友的后面, 他们也没注意\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}She was following behind her friends,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but they didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.95,0:11:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们会来找我的  - 坐下\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- They'll come looking for me.  - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,凶手!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须给我们放尊重点, 回答我的问题\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You'll have to show us some respect\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在那个航线上工作?   - 我没明白\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Which airline do you work for?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定属于某条航线, 或者这里的机场管理方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You must belong to an airline\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}or the airport authority to be in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟机场没有任何关系, 只是刚抵达这里, 迷路了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got nothing to do with the airport.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'd just arrived. We were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我正想找人帮忙, 然后就看到他杀了一个人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I was trying to find someone to help me,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and I saw him kill a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.46,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你们刚抵达这里? 你怎么到这里的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You say you'd just arrived? How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从她这里问不出什么来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'll gain nothing by questioning her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是我们抓住了她\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The important thing is that we've got her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不会觉得我的朋友们就这样把我给忘了吧, 会吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You don't think my friends\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}are just going to forget me like that, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂了, 博士, 那儿都找不到 Polly\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}I don't understand it, Doctor.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Polly's nowhere to be seen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定出什么事了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}Something must have happened to her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这里锁住的, Jamie, 里面没人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&\i1}That's locked, Jamie. There's nobody there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心我们是在浪费时间, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm afraid we're wasting our time here, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们越早找到当局越好, 把情况告诉他们. 快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The sooner we find the authorities\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and tell it to them, the better. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 你说得对. 你的朋友们的确在担心你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, you're right.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Your friends ARE worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.22,0:12:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们必须得做点什么, 让他们不要再担心了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Then we shall have to do something\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to stop them worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来是往这边, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This seems to be the way, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了. 我们在找这里的负责人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excuse me. We're looking for someone in authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下, 先生. 都来得及的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Just a moment, sir. All in good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你, 女士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 先生, 请出示你们的护照\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, sir. Your passport, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我没时间说这个, 我们要找负责人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got no time for that.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We want to see someone in authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是负责人. 请出示你的护照\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am in authority. Your passport, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你没搞明白, 我们有一些重要情况要报告\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You don't understand.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We have something important to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以, 先生, 但得等你们找到了护照再说\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, sir, when you've found your passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个, 请过来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Next one, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 护照是什么, 博士?  - 官方要的某种叽叽歪歪的东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What's a passport, Doctor?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Some sort of official mumbo-jumbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听着, 我们刚刚在那边发现了一具尸体\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Look, we've just discovered a dead body out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你听到我说话了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,听到了, 先生. 如果我是你, 就会通知警方\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, sir. If I were you, I'd inform the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我在哪里可以找到他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Please tell me where we can find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在大厅里应该就有一个警察\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There's probably a policeman in the main concourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大厅在哪儿?  - 从这个门过去往左拐\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- And where is that?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Through this door and turn to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢, 非常感谢. 走吧, Jamie\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you, thank you very much. Come on, Jamie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看你的护照吗, 先生?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}May I see your passport, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩谁都没有护照!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We neither of us have passports!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你满意了吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Does that satisfy you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你肯定搞错了, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think you must be mistaken, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有护照是不可能登上飞机的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You couldn't have got on the aircraft without passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么飞机?   - 你们坐着抵达这里的飞机, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What aircraft?  - The one you arrived on, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是坐着飞机抵达的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We didn't arrive on an aircraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好了, 听着, 这个玩笑开得有点过头了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, look here, this joke's gone far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知我也知, 你们肯定是搭乘刚才进港这个航班抵达的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You know and I know that you must have arrived\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}on the last inbound flight
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 而这个航班729来自马德里  - 告诉他 TARDIS 的事情\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- which was flight 729 from Madrid\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Tell him about the Tardis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是什么?   - 是我们到达这里的方法\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What's that?  - It's the way we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两位绅士不会碰巧知道一个警察亭子吧, 知道吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You gentlemen wouldn't know anything\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}about a police box, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的就是这个. 我们就是...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That's what I'm saying! We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的觉得我们的交通方式跟这个无关\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I really think that our mode\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}of conveyance is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的事情是我们在外面发现了一具尸体!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The important thing is that\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}we discovered a dead body out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们想把这事报告给这里的负责人!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And we want to report it to someone in authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你们有很多机会跟负责人见面\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I think you'll have plenty of opportunity\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}to see someone in authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好, 谢谢你, 非常感谢  - 你们能坐一会儿吗, 那边\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Well, thank you. Thank you very much.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will you take a seat, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接总指挥, 谢谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Give me the commandant, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你好, 长官. 我是Jenkins, 出入境五号柜台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello, sir. Jenkins here. Immigration desk five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我这里有两个你说那种嫌疑人员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've got two of your suspects here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有人吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近应该有人啊. 这里有人吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There must be someone around. Anyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗, Blade 机长在吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Hello. Is Captain Blade about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道, 我有点迷路了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I don't know. I'm a bit lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在找我吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我这里有你的飞行排班表, 都安排好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I have your flight schedules here.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They're all in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢    - 再见\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Thank you.  - Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你有什么需要吗?   - 我在找出口\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What do you want?  - I'm looking for the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.74,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是私人物业, 不欢迎游客\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is private property. Visitors are not welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你是机场方面的吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you belong to the airport staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是, 我今天刚上班\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yeah. I started today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是故意来这里的, 只是走迷路了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I didn't mean to come in here. I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你确定?   - 当然确定\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Are you sure?  - Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你还打算带我出去不?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you going to direct me or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当然, 来吧, 我给你指路\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, of course. Come on. I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你说这个女孩儿目击了一场谋杀?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You say this girl witnessed a murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 她看见那个男人被杀了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, she saw the man killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那人被一把射线枪给电死了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He was electrocuted with a ray gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一把什么?   - 哦, 是什么枪又有什么关系\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A what?  - Oh, what does it matter what sort of gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.61,0:15:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是他被杀了, 而我的朋友又目睹了事情经过\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The point is he was killed and my friend saw it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那你朋友在哪儿? 我想跟她谈谈\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Where is she? I'd like to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个, 又是另外一件事了, 她消失了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, that's another thing. She's vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 消失的人, 射线枪. 这是某种玩笑吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, people who vanish, ray guns...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Is this some sort of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你见到尸体就不会觉得这是个玩笑了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You wouldn't think it a joke if you saw the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是坐哪趟航班来的?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What flight did they come in on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.51,0:16:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,长官, 他们是跟马德里729航班的乘客一起进来的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, sir, they came in with the passengers\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}from flight 729 from Madrid,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们没有护照\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}but they've no passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你们可以解释一下, 你们为什么没有护照\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Perhaps you'd kindly explain why you have no passports.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 天, 我们完全是在浪费时间!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, look, we're all wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还去不去看尸体了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Are you going to come and see that body, or am I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是我得去找这个地方真正的负责人?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}going to find someone\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}who really is in charge in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这里的负责人, 谢谢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I am in charge of this place, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 你们俩立刻陪我去这个机库\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, you both accompany me to this hangar immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢, 非常感谢你. 终于!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you! Thank you very much. At last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把我的去向告诉航空控制台  - 是, 先生\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Tell Air Traffic Control where I am.  - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是出入境五号柜台\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Immigration desk five here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一号已经刚往机库去了, 他期望我告诉你们这个信息\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Number One's just gone to the hangar area.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He wanted me to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上, 他是去找一具死尸\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}As a matter of fact,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}he's just gone to look for a dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊, 总会有这么一天的, 对吧?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, It's gonna be one of those days, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 搞定她了?   - 她已经被处理了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Get her?  - She's being processed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下一航班他们可以再带一个了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}They can take another on the next flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.66,0:17:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体 - 不见了!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The body - it's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能肯定就是这个机库?   - 是, 名字都在外面呢\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You're quite sure you've got the right hangar?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Aye. The name's up outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.19,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体刚才就躺在这里\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The body was lying just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那, 那我们看看能找到什么, 行吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Well, let's see what we HAVE got, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底是在做什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What exactly are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是在帮警察找线索啊\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}For the police, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于我没法告诉他们那人是谁\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The trouble is I can't tell them who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,某种神秘人物, 肯定无疑\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Some sort of mystery man, no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 事实上他真是\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, as a matter of fact he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他口袋里没有任何东西可以表明他的身份\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There was nothing in his pockets to identify him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 一个口袋里没有任何东西的人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, a man with nothing in his pockets
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我也觉得很诧异\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, I was rather surprised myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等等, 还真有个东西\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Wait. There WAS one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他口袋里有什么?   - 这个\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- What did he have in his pocket?  - This.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一张邮票?   - 但它是西班牙的, 而且还没有用过\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- A postage stamp.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- But it's Spanish and it hasn't been used.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 我肯定这就有很大的不同了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, I'm sure that'll make all the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,的确. 哈罗...这有点意思\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Exactly. Hello... This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在发现了什么?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What have you found now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一丝被烧焦的纤维\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's burnt fibres.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这说明什么, 博士?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What about this, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才这里并没有, 这里有个烧焦的痕迹\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This wasn't here before. It's a burn mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对, Jamie, 这是新的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You're right, Jamie. It's quite new.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,能见到有人肯动动脑, 真是高兴\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's good to see someone is using their intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,噢, 我受够这些了! 你们俩跟我来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, I've had enough of this!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You two coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对是射线枪造成的\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Definitely made by a ray gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,射线枪, 烧焦的纤维, 外国邮票\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Ray gun, burnt fibres, foreign stamps...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没用过的外国邮票 - 好, 没用过的外国邮票\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Unused foreign stamps.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- All right, unused foreign stamps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定是跟你一样疯了, 还在听你瞎说!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I must be as mad as you are,\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}even to be listening to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你知道他们把它怎么样了么?   - 把什么怎么样了?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- You know what they've done with it?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Done with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体. 在某个地方肯定有一个很大的行李箱\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}The body. Somewhere there's a large packing case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就在你后面, 博士\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Right behind you, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要我帮忙吗?  - 你是变色龙观光团的吗\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Can I help you?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Are you connected with Chameleon Tours?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的, 我是机长Blade, 首席飞行员\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes. I'm Captain Blade - chief pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这两位绅士觉得...\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}These gentlemen think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- ...这里发生了一场事故. - 事故?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- ...there's an incident happened in here.  - An incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你介意我们看一下这个行李箱里面吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Would you mind if we have a look in this packing case?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 冒昧问一下, 你是哪位?  - 我是机场总指挥\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- May I ask who you are?  - I'm the commandant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可以, 当然可以\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们指望找到什么呢?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}What do you expect to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一个死人\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}A dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真有意思\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}How very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,塑料杯!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Plastic cups!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我得做点自己的调查工作了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now I'm going to do some investigating of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴终于激起了你的兴趣!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I'm glad I've roused your interest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦, 的确是, 不过我打算调查的是你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Oh, you have. But what I'm going to investigate is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你俩为什么会出现在机场\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}and why you're both here in the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你, Blade 机长. 来吧, 你俩, 出去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Thank you, Captain Blade. Come on, you two. Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最好迁就一下他\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We'd better humour him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把他弄下来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Bring him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他能活下来吗?  - 如果我们动作快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Will he survive? - If we hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.65,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就这里了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得把你弄到机场大楼去\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}We've got to get you to the airport building.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就安全了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}And you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你快要到窒息点了, 快点\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}He's reaching suffocation point. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你都没有让我好好搜查\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}You didn't let me search properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个机库出租给了一个私有承包公司\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}That hangar is leased to a private charter company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我都无权在那里进行搜查, 更别说你了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've have no right to search in there, let alone you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在, 你可否坐下来, 保持安静?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Now, will you kindly sit down and keep quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenkins, 给我接 Reynolds 警司\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Jenkins, get onto Superintendent Reynolds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的活儿, 这些人在这里乱闯\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}This is his job. These people are trespassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我这里刚有另外一家飞机抵港  - 好吧, 我自己来\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- I've just got another flight coming through.\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- All right. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.37,0:20:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,博士, 你看!\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Doctor, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,总指挥, 这就是我刚跟你说的那个女孩\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Commandant, this is the girl I was telling you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I beg your pardon?\N你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识这两位先生吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}Do you know these gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不认识, 怎么了, 该认识吗?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- No. Why? Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 据他们说, 他们认识你\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- According to them, they know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你去哪儿了, Polly?   - Polly?\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}- Where have you been, Polly?  - Polly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不叫 Polly,  你们肯定搞错了\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}My name isn't Polly. You must have made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我这辈子从没有见过他们\N{\fs14\c&HC0C0C0&}I've never seen them before in my life.
